<title>LET GOD JOIN THEM TOGETHER</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien in atung in kichen hi A siem,
 Inkuon bul thiengtho umkhawm dingin;
 Kipanpih, kizah a, ginum gel gel din,
 Hin kithengin a bukim na'ng un.

[V2]
 Lawp takin kipahpih chiet hitiu,
 I suohpihteu kichenna thu hi;
 Zien I hetpih u hih Lalpa'n zawm det hen,
 Thihna lo chun kuoma'n khen kihen.

[V3]
 2. A det zie chuh genin, Lal Isu'n A tii,
 &quot;A nu leh pa hun nusieu un tin;
 Chawnbana kiluoi in, pumkhat hung hi'n au,
 Michuom ei puou pumkhat a hung hi'u.&quot;

[V4]
 3. A det ding zie mai chuh Lal Isu'n a tii,
 &quot;Pathien gawp chuh kuoman khen kihen&quot;
 Pumkhat ahi tau hi lei leh van hetin,
 Kilungsiet na'n kizawm det uhen.

[V5]
 4. Isun A Sapchuomte A hehpih bang khan,
 A hinna amau A piek bangin;
 Zie monei dingpa hin le hehpih hen la,
 Tehkal thu thieng hi ngai gel uhen.

[V6]
 5. Lalpa, amau nih hi Na khutah vawpin,
 Liehkhuh in Na phatnan vuk inla;
 Lungkham leh kipah hun in kihet sakin,
 Na piek, nasepna dingin pieu hen.</lyrics>
</song>